<div id="review_2485998049" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2485998049" />
    <a title="Jan Philipzig" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/32295170-jan-philipzig"><img alt="Jan Philipzig" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1412522099p2/32295170.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2485998049?book_show_action=true">Aug 07, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jan Philipzig" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jan Philipzig" href="/user/show/32295170-jan-philipzig">Jan Philipzig</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=poverty">poverty</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=mass-media">mass-media</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=politics">politics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=crime">crime</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=documentary">documentary</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=globalization">globalization</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=surveillance">surveillance</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2485998049" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17028164700368781801">Investigative journalism at its best! Jane Mayer&apos;s meticulously researched book takes a close look at a crucially important topic that is largely being ignored by the mainstream media: the fact that a few rather secretive (American, not Russian) billionaires are in the process of hijacking American democracy for their own selfish ends. Essential reading for anybody who has been wondering what the FUCK is going on.</span>
  <span id="freeText17028164700368781801" style="display:none">Investigative journalism at its best! Jane Mayer's meticulously researched book takes a close look at a crucially important topic that is largely being ignored by the mainstream media: the fact that a few rather secretive (American, not Russian) billionaires are in the process of hijacking American democracy for their own selfish ends. Essential reading for anybody who has been wondering what the FUCK is going on.</span>
  <a data-text-id="17028164700368781801" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


