<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/56269283-wildland"><img alt="Wildland: The Making of America&#39;s Fury" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1616477635l/56269283._SX98_.jpg" />
