<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/54549370-kill-switch"><img alt="Kill Switch: The Rise of the Modern Senate and the Crippling of American Democracy" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1595602521l/54549370._SX98_.jpg" />
